      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I hear what you're saying about the real world, but that's the thing. Even when i go outside, it's the same. I'm just another person passing by. I don't have anyone to call or text to tell them where I am. It doesn't feel like I'm part of anything. It just feels like I'm waiting for something to finish. It's like I'm already halfway gone.",
